---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About - Matt Wright">
  <a href="/" class="back-link">← back</a>

  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>Matt Wright</h1>
      <p class="about-role">CEO & Co-founder, EVM Systems</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-links-row">
      <a href="https://x.com/mateo_ventures" target="_blank">X / Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mateoventures" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/MateoDev" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://warpcast.com/mateoventures" target="_blank">Farcaster</a>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">

      <p>Matt Wright is CEO and Co-founder of <a href="https://evmsystems.ai" target="_blank">EVM Systems</a>, building agentic infrastructure and products for the agent economy. The thesis: self-owned AI requires three layers — open models and inference (<a href="https://gaianet.ai" target="_blank">Gaia</a>), agentic infrastructure (<a href="https://xo.ai" target="_blank">XO</a>), and local compute (<a href="https://one.olares.com/" target="_blank">Olares</a>). EVM Systems sits at the center of this stack, shipping products for startups, enterprise, and Web3.</p>

      <p>Matt co-founded <a href="https://gaianet.ai" target="_blank">Gaia</a>, a decentralized open-source AI infrastructure network that grew to 710,000+ nodes, 30+ trillion inferences, and 110+ strategic integrations with partners including Coinbase, EigenLayer, ENS, MetaMask/Consensys, and Moonpay. He led the project from concept through a <a href="https://www.taisu.io/centralized-ai-is-eating-the-world-but-what-if-users-owned-the-intelligence/" target="_blank">$20M raise</a>, token launch, the Gaia AI Phone on Samsung Galaxy S25, and the formation of the Gaia Foundation and DAO.</p>

      <p>At <a href="https://consensys.io" target="_blank">Consensys</a>, Matt held multiple leadership roles — Director of Developer Relations, Director of Decentralized Community &amp; DAOs, and Director of the Fellowship Program. He shaped developer GTM and token economics strategies for 400k+ developers across products like MetaMask and Infura.</p>

      <p>At <a href="https://www.jpmorgan.com" target="_blank">J.P. Morgan</a>, Matt bootstrapped a developer community around Quorum, the open-source enterprise Ethereum platform. He built a 50+ member global Ambassador program across 25+ countries and drove the visibility that laid the groundwork for <a href="https://consensys.io/blog/consensys-acquires-quorum-platform-from-jp-morgan" target="_blank">Quorum's acquisition by Consensys</a>.</p>

      <p>At <a href="https://angelhack.com" target="_blank">AngelHack</a>, as Director of Community Development, he grew the global developer base from 50k to 200k members across 75+ countries. His team organized 150+ hackathons for Fortune 500 companies including Mastercard, Motorola, ABInBev, RBC, Barclays, and UBS.</p>

      <p>Outside of these roles, Matt co-founded <a href="https://daonyc.xyz" target="_blank">DAO NYC</a> and <a href="https://wgmi.io" target="_blank">Wgmi</a>, and has organized some of the most memorable events in crypto — including the Korea Blockchain Week Official Afterparty with <a href="https://chris-lake.com/" target="_blank">Chris Lake</a>, Metahills in Beverly Hills with <a href="https://tokimonsta.com/" target="_blank">TOKiMONSTA</a>, Gn at NFT NYC with <a href="https://claudevonstroke.com/" target="_blank">Claude VonStroke</a> (<a href="https://time.com/6115274/nft-conference-parties-culture/" target="_blank">featured in TIME</a>), and the Gaia Launch Party at Token2049 with <a href="https://www.diplo.com/" target="_blank">Diplo</a>. He is a member of <a href="https://www.metacartel.org/" target="_blank">MetaCartel DAO</a> and has contributed to 25+ DAOs.</p>

      <hr />

      <h2>Press</h2>
      <ul class="press-list">
        <li><a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/amyguttman/2025/09/01/the-founder-betting-on-a-decentralized-future-for-ai/" target="_blank">Forbes</a> — The Founder Betting on a Decentralized Future for AI</li>
        <li><a href="https://cointelegraph.com/news/web3-gaia-hardware-crypto-phones-consoles" target="_blank">Cointelegraph</a> — Web3, Gaia, Hardware, Crypto Phones</li>
        <li><a href="https://decrypt.co/297060/gaia-is-building-living-knowledge-systems-for-ai-agents" target="_blank">Decrypt</a> — Gaia is Building Living Knowledge Systems for AI Agents</li>
        <li><a href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/gaianet-secures-10m-build-decentralized-183000076.html" target="_blank">Yahoo Finance</a> — GaiaNet Secures $10M to Build Decentralized AI</li>
        <li><a href="https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/stocks/gaia-partners-with-eigenlayer-to-bring-powerful-avs-security-to-decentralized-ai-1033946119" target="_blank">Business Insider</a> — Gaia Partners with EigenLayer</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.theblock.co/post/252044/consensys-web3-fellowship-program-fund" target="_blank">The Block</a> — Consensys Web3 Fellowship Program</li>
        <li><a href="https://time.com/6115274/nft-conference-parties-culture/" target="_blank">TIME</a> — NFT Conference Parties Culture</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Speaking</h2>
      <ul class="press-list">
        <li><a href="https://consensus2025.coindesk.com/agenda/speaker/-matt-wright" target="_blank">Consensus 2025</a></li>
        <li>Token2049</li>
        <li>ETHDenver</li>
        <li>Korea Blockchain Week</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SWaU8b4tthw" target="_blank">MIT</a></li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <p class="contact-line">Get in touch: <a href="mailto:matt@evmsystems.ai">matt@evmsystems.ai</a></p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-wrap {
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--faint);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 1.1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-role {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-links-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .about-links-row a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid var(--faint);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }

  .about-links-row a:hover {
    color: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .contact-line {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-line a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.4em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .about-body a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: var(--faint);
  }

  .about-body a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--ink);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .about-body hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--faint);
    margin: 2.5em 0;
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
  }

  .press-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2em 0;
  }

  .press-list li {
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--faint);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .press-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .press-list a {
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .press-list a:hover {
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .about-links-row { gap: 12px; }
    .about-body { font-size: 15px; }
  }
</style>
